      ▷ (£ 1 ={∅,E}=∗
        state_interp sigma (S ns) ks nt ∗
        (pico_lr_threadI
          sΓ sΓ mt tail (loc, cache_f) derived abs_vals -∗
          WP tail @ s; E {{ Φ }})))
    -∗ WP full @ s; E {{ Φ }}.
  Proof.
    simpl.
