        ⌜wm_cache_history_state sigma addr derived abs_vals ->
          wm_cache_history_state sigma' addr derived abs_vals⌝ -∗
        £ 1 ={∅,E}=∗
        state_interp sigma' (S ns) ks nt ∗
        WP e' @ s; E {{ Φ }})
