      abs_vals ={E}=∗
    pico_cache_state_interp
      N'
      (mkWMConfig sigma' [mkWMThread rΓ SSkip V'])
      addr
      derived
      abs_vals.
  Proof.
    iIntros (Hsubset Hx Hy Hwrite) "Hstmt Hstate".
    unfold pico_lr_stmtI, pico_sem_typed_stmt_cacheI.
    iDestruct "Hstmt" as %[Htyping Hsafe].
    iApply (pico_cache_state_interp_after_fldwrite_step with "Hstate");
      eauto.
  Qed.

