      (loc, cache_f)
      derived
      abs_vals.
  Proof.
    iIntros (Hsubset) "Hspec Hbridge".
    unfold pico_wp_state_cfg_bridge.
    iDestruct "Hbridge" as "(_ & Hstate)".
    iMod (pico_lr_cache_update_execution_specI_state_after_execution
      E N N' sΓ mt rΓ loc cache_f receiver tmp derived abs_vals n Vthread
      sigma threads i cfg' Hsubset with "Hspec Hstate")
